Project Summary

Project Information

Field Value
Name Automatic Library
Description A system backing a simple robotic library encompassing a shelf-mounted series of servomotors that help to deliver the requested book to the user, in addition to the capability to return a book to the system without having to worry about alphabetizing by title or sorting by a cataloging system.
Homepage https://rawgit.com/chadnach1/TeamAutoLib/master/target/site/index.html
